snippet.title: Amber Heard & Johnny Depp: The Real ABUSER FINALLY REVEALED!! (UNCENSORED AUDIO!) #JUSTICEFORJOHNNY
snippet.description:
This is a recorded conversation/argument between Johnny Depp and Amber Heard.  This was recorded just months before they filed for divorce in May 2016.

I know this is a long one, but I encourage you to listen to/watch the entire video.  I feel this finally confirms who the real abuser was in this relationship, and the audio speaks for itself, although I do add some context and insight...but try to keep it to minimum.
